</tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lord Ruthermont</b> was an <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> lord during the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Ruthermont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_Invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal Invasion\">Andal Invasion</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a>, Lord Ruthermont was part of the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> coalition led by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Artys_I_Arryn\" title=\"Artys I Arryn\">Artys Arryn</a>. He fought in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Seven_Stars\" title=\"Battle of the Seven Stars\">Battle of the Seven Stars</a> and some named him as the killer of King <a href=\"/index.php/Robar_II_Royce\" title=\"Robar II Royce\">Robar II Royce</a>, the leader of the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> coalition.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Ruthermont&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404214716\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.078 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.279 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 488/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10438/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4850/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 330/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 842/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  270.086      1 -total\n 97.07%  262.164      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.34%  260.188      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.44%   33.602     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.81%   12.988      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.26%    6.116      2 Template:Ref\n  1.39%    3.745      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.58%    1.568      1 Template:References\n  0.37%    1.009      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>